{"tid":2461421,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"不只歐陽娜娜挺新疆棉 解約台藝人曝","createTime":"2021-03-25T11:47:17.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-25T11:55:40.000Z","uid":85180,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"bc743e5ebb194c365787495bfcfd54e9d99c07c2","tid":2461421,"uid":85180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T11:47:17.000Z","msg":"不只歐陽娜娜挺新疆棉 解約台藝人曝<br />\n三立新聞網<br />\n2021年3月25日 週四 下午7:10&middot;2 分鐘 (閱讀時間)<br />\n娛樂中心／綜合報導<br />\n<br />\nH&amp;M在23日宣布將停止與中國工廠合作，主要是考量新疆人權議題，停止使用新疆的產品或原材料，其中就包括棉花，聲明一出立刻引發中國網友反彈，連帶許多國際品牌Nike、adidas、Zara、Converse、Calvin Klein等都被「獵巫」，中國大陸的明星也紛紛跳出來宣布解約，讓網友們忍不住高喊「國家利益高於一切，愛國不是說說而已」<br />\n歐陽娜娜被網友質疑為何還不解約「滾回台灣」後，工作室趕緊在微博發出聲明，「即日起，我司及我司藝人歐陽娜娜女士終止與『CONVERSE匡威』品牌的一切合作。我司及歐陽娜娜女士堅決抵制任何污化中國的言論與行為，國家尊嚴不容侵犯，堅決維護祖國利益」，中國網友大讚「支持歐陽娜娜，政治立場一直很堅定」、「國家尊嚴不容侵犯，歐陽娜娜和歐陽娜娜的粉絲堅決維護祖國利益」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/RbLPv6cBEaF.oCnHce08gQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTUzOS44MjYwODY5NTY1MjE3O2NmPXdlYnA-/https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/65Ti.hnyYKCuB6F_aXflkw--~B/aD0zODg7dz02OTA7YXBwaWQ9eXRhY2h5b24-/https://media.zenfs.com/en/setn.com.tw/3a2c2e14aa6ec46bb1f26476ea914783\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FRbLPv6cBEaF.oCnHce08gQ--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTUzOS44MjYwODY5NTY1MjE3O2NmPXdlYnA-%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fuu%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F65Ti.hnyYKCuB6F_aXflkw--~B%2FaD0zODg7dz02OTA7YXBwaWQ9eXRhY2h5b24-%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Fsetn.com.tw%2F3a2c2e14aa6ec46bb1f26476ea914783&h=ce85debd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n歐陽娜娜工作室宣布與Converse終止合作。（圖／翻攝自歐陽娜娜工作室微博）<br />\n除了歐陽娜娜之外，其他台灣藝人的工作室，也陸續在微博發出解約聲明，彭于晏工作室、張鈞甯工作室宣布終止和adidas品牌的一切合作，北京合力極光文化傳媒有限公司也PO出2張聲明，內容提到「我司及合作藝人許光漢先生」終止和PUMA、Calvin Klein合作，「我們堅決反對任何污化中國的言論與行徑」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/jCiLYm551UtBtdp_Xj1NJQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTEyNzI7Y2Y9d2VicA--/https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/2aNw4UGLl3s9.YCd4VkEuA--~B/aD0xMDYwO3c9ODAwO2FwcGlkPXl0YWNoeW9u/https://media.zenfs.com/en/setn.com.tw/2d23a81833f80c2026cf49aaf0aac312\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FjCiLYm551UtBtdp_Xj1NJQ--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTEyNzI7Y2Y9d2VicA--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fuu%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F2aNw4UGLl3s9.YCd4VkEuA--~B%2FaD0xMDYwO3c9ODAwO2FwcGlkPXl0YWNoeW9u%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Fsetn.com.tw%2F2d23a81833f80c2026cf49aaf0aac312&h=68440ac4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n彭于晏宣布解約。（圖／翻攝自彭于晏工作室微博）<br />\n至於賴冠霖和陳立農也「態度明確」表達「支持新疆棉花」的立場，前者更被爆原本腳上穿Converse和Nike，但在「新疆棉」事件持續發燒後，只好改穿一雙黑色拖鞋趕飛機，被中國網友狂讚「哈哈哈哈，好可愛我的天」、「賴冠霖真的是很有危機意識了」、「太有魅力了」。<br />\n<br />\n以下是截至3月25日18:30的解約名單<br />\n<br />\nH&amp;M：黃軒、宋茜<br />\nNike：王一博、譚松韻<br />\nConverse：張藝興、白敬亭、歐陽娜娜<br />\nadidas：易烊千璽、楊冪、迪麗熱巴、Angelababy、彭于晏、王嘉爾、陳立農、鄧倫、丁禹兮、彭昱暢、任敏、宋妍霏、張鈞甯、陳奕迅<br />\nUniqlo：井柏然、雷佳音、倪妮、王源<br />\nPUMA：李現、劉昊然、古力娜扎、許光漢、楊洋<br />\nCK：張藝興、劉雨昕、許光漢<br />\nNewBalance：孟美岐、張子楓<br />\nTommyHilfiger解約：陳偉霆、李振寧"},{"pid":"7ed73240d43eac84e9ba309491ee7127aeb98e39","tid":2461421,"uid":237562,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T11:49:40.000Z","msg":"垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42af2e5e4db1128dfa5b0479fce896d14599b914","tid":2461421,"uid":375787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T11:51:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/jES3jUn7O44\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FjES3jUn7O44&d=Vr1Lb3BWhK3V%2BSmIqtN%2B%2FsjT01h1KCp2%2Bw2KB0oDRGE%3D&h=8542a9e1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/jES3jUn7O44</a>"},{"pid":"3f4ad8d3384f63b5d44663404ed8001d239052da","tid":2461421,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T11:51:46.000Z","msg":"垃撚圾"},{"pid":"0a6e6a617db8b7a2fc31b1550